<h2>     
ATTENTION: NEW ADDRESS 
 
</h2>
 




 </div> </div>
 
   <div class='uniblock' style="width:780px;">
    <div class='uniblock_text' style=" float:left; padding-bottom:0px; padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px; padding-top:0px;
									  margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:199px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:20px; width:255px; text-align:left; line-height:140%;">
 
 
 The  address  of Azerbaijanian film festival in Armenia was changed. <br><br>Festival will pass at 1 Pavstos Biuzand Blvd (Vernissage, near the Center for Contemporary Experimental Art)
 
<br><br>
 <strong>Georgi Vanyan<br>
 11.11.2010</strong>
	 		
	 	 <div style="border:1px solid #999;  height:0px; width:253px; margin-bottom:27px; margin-top:20px;"> </div>	
	 		
